###### load_B = {load_B_through_A, load_B_through_PS}
###### assert 10 to load through A, 01 to load through PS
###### assert 00 to compute, and 11 undefined

### load B = 3, A propagates, B sets top 8 bits to 0 and propagates
#SEND  |  load_B  |       A_in      |        shared_B_PS_in
0001______01__________00101100_________10111000_00000011
#RECV  |  0  |      A_out           |        shared_B_PS_out
0010______00__________00101100_________00000000_00000011

### feed A = 5, PS = 25, PS_out = 5 * 3 + 25 = 40
